{"tha-ap541:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap541:0.2":"Kaccayanavagga ","tha-ap541:0.3":"Radhattheraapadana ","tha-ap541:1.1":"“Padumuttaro nama jino, ","tha-ap541:1.2":"sabbalokavidu muni; ","tha-ap541:1.3":"Ito satasahassamhi, ","tha-ap541:1.4":"kappe uppajji cakkhuma. ","tha-ap541:2.1":"Ovadako vinnapako, ","tha-ap541:2.2":"tarako sabbapaninam; ","tha-ap541:2.3":"Desanakusalo buddho, ","tha-ap541:2.4":"taresi janatam bahum. ","tha-ap541:3.1":"Anukampako karuniko, ","tha-ap541:3.2":"hitesi sabbapaninam; ","tha-ap541:3.3":"Sampatte titthiye sabbe, ","tha-ap541:3.4":"pancasile patitthapi. ","tha-ap541:4.1":"Evam nirakulam asi, ","tha-ap541:4.2":"sunnatam titthiyehi ca; ","tha-ap541:4.3":"Vicittam arahantehi, ","tha-ap541:4.4":"vasibhutehi tadibhi. ","tha-ap541:5.1":"Ratananatthapannasam, ","tha-ap541:5.2":"uggato so mahamuni; ","tha-ap541:5.3":"Kancanagghiyasankaso, ","tha-ap541:5.4":"battimsavaralakkhano. ","tha-ap541:6.1":"Vassasatasahassani, ","tha-ap541:6.2":"ayu vijjati tavade; ","tha-ap541:6.3":"Tavata titthamano so, ","tha-ap541:6.4":"taresi janatam bahum. ","tha-ap541:7.1":"Tadaham hamsavatiyam, ","tha-ap541:7.2":"brahmano mantaparagu; ","tha-ap541:7.3":"Upecca tam naravaram, ","tha-ap541:7.4":"assosim dhammadesanam. ","tha-ap541:8.1":"Pannapentam mahaviram, ","tha-ap541:8.2":"parisasu visaradam; ","tha-ap541:8.3":"Patibhaneyyakam bhikkhum, ","tha-ap541:8.4":"etadagge vinayakam. ","tha-ap541:9.1":"Tadaham karam katvana, ","tha-ap541:9.2":"sasanghe lokanayake; ","tha-ap541:9.3":"Nipacca sirasa pade, ","tha-ap541:9.4":"tam thanam abhipatthayim. ","tha-ap541:10.1":"Tato mam bhagava aha, ","tha-ap541:10.2":"singinikkhasamappabho; ","tha-ap541:10.3":"Sarena rajaniyena, ","tha-ap541:10.4":"kilesamalaharina. ","tha-ap541:11.1":"‘Sukhi bhavassu dighayu, ","tha-ap541:11.2":"sijjhatu panidhi tava; ","tha-ap541:11.3":"Sasanghe me katam karam, ","tha-ap541:11.4":"ativa vipulam taya. ","tha-ap541:12.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap541:12.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap541:12.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap541:12.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap541:13.1":"Tassa dhammesu dayado, ","tha-ap541:13.2":"oraso dhammanimmito; ","tha-ap541:13.3":"Radhoti namadheyyena, ","tha-ap541:13.4":"hessati satthu savako. ","tha-ap541:14.1":"Sa te hetugune tuttho, ","tha-ap541:14.2":"sakyaputto narasabho; ","tha-ap541:14.3":"Patibhaneyyakanaggam, ","tha-ap541:14.4":"pannapessati nayako’. ","tha-ap541:15.1":"Tam sutva mudito hutva, ","tha-ap541:15.2":"yavajivam tada jinam; ","tha-ap541:15.3":"Mettacitto paricarim, ","tha-ap541:15.4":"sato pannasamahito. ","tha-ap541:16.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","tha-ap541:16.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","tha-ap541:16.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","tha-ap541:16.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","tha-ap541:17.1":"Satanam tinikkhattunca, ","tha-ap541:17.2":"devarajjamakarayim; ","tha-ap541:17.3":"Satanam pancakkhattunca, ","tha-ap541:17.4":"cakkavatti ahosaham. ","tha-ap541:18.1":"Padesarajjam vipulam, ","tha-ap541:18.2":"gananato asankhiyam; ","tha-ap541:18.3":"Sabbattha sukhito asim, ","tha-ap541:18.4":"tassa kammassa vahasa. ","tha-ap541:19.1":"Pacchime bhave sampatte, ","tha-ap541:19.2":"giribbajapuruttame; ","tha-ap541:19.3":"Jato vippakule niddhe, ","tha-ap541:19.4":"vikalacchadanasane. ","tha-ap541:20.1":"Katacchubhikkham padasim, ","tha-ap541:20.2":"sariputtassa tadino; ","tha-ap541:20.3":"Yada jinno ca vuddho ca, ","tha-ap541:20.4":"tadaramamupagamim. ","tha-ap541:21.1":"Pabbajati na mam koci, ","tha-ap541:21.2":"jinnadubbalathamakam; ","tha-ap541:21.3":"Tena dino vivannango, ","tha-ap541:21.4":"soko casim tada aham. ","tha-ap541:22.1":"Disva mahakaruniko, ","tha-ap541:22.2":"mamamaha mahamuni; ","tha-ap541:22.3":"‘Kimattham puttasokatto, ","tha-ap541:22.4":"bruhi te cittajam rujam’. ","tha-ap541:23.1":"‘Pabbajjam na labhe vira, ","tha-ap541:23.2":"svakkhate tava sasane; ","tha-ap541:23.3":"Tena sokena dinosmi, ","tha-ap541:23.4":"saranam hohi nayaka’. ","tha-ap541:24.1":"Tada bhikkhu samanetva, ","tha-ap541:24.2":"apucchi munisattamo; ","tha-ap541:24.3":"‘Imassa adhikaram ye, ","tha-ap541:24.4":"saranti byaharantu te’. ","tha-ap541:25.1":"Sariputto tadavoca, ","tha-ap541:25.2":"‘karamassa saramaham; ","tha-ap541:25.3":"Katacchubhikkham dapesi, ","tha-ap541:25.4":"pindaya carato mama’. ","tha-ap541:26.1":"‘Sadhu sadhu katannusi, ","tha-ap541:26.2":"sariputta imam tuvam; ","tha-ap541:26.3":"Pabbajehi dijam vuddham, ","tha-ap541:26.4":"hessatajaniyo ayam’. ","tha-ap541:27.1":"Tato alattham pabbajjam, ","tha-ap541:27.2":"kammavacopasampadam; ","tha-ap541:27.3":"Na cireneva kalena, ","tha-ap541:27.4":"papunim asavakkhayam. ","tha-ap541:28.1":"Sakkaccam munino vakyam, ","tha-ap541:28.2":"sunami mudito yato; ","tha-ap541:28.3":"Patibhaneyyakanaggam, ","tha-ap541:28.4":"tato mam thapayi jino. ","tha-ap541:29.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap541:29.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap541:29.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap541:30.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap541:30.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap541:30.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap541:31.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap541:31.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap541:31.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap541:32.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma radho thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap541:33.1":"Radhattherassapadanam navamam. "}